                            <h1 class="text-xs-center author-heading">About Us</h1>
                            <div class="author-profile-box">
                                <p class="author-top-content">
                                    We are dedicated to providing a free place for people around the world to share
                                    their stories. Everyone has a story to tell. A good story can make us laugh or cry,
                                    or stand up and cheer, or maybe just nod our heads in recognition, because we can
                                    relate. A good story can help us see things in a new way. Stories can entertain us,
                                    enlighten us, and they can change us. Our lives are full of stories; stories of joy
                                    and sorrow, triumph and tragedy, success and failure. The stories of our lives
                                    matter. Share them. Sharing the stories of our lives with each other can bring us
                                    closer together and help us get to know one another better. Thank you for visiting
                                    Storystar. Please invite your friends and family to visit us to read and rate all
                                    the wonderful stories that have been published here, and to tell their stories too.
                                </p>
                                <p class="author-top-content pt-0">StoryStar headquarters are located on the central
                                    Oregon coast. </p>
